data.description: Beautiful historical home in downtown Marianna within walking distance to most everything! (ZONED MIXED USE) Main home is 3/2 with an office/bonus room that could be an extra bedroom. New appliances installed and bathroom remodeled by current owners!! There is also a separate ''mother in law suite''/studio type apartment here with a living area, kitchen, and full bathroom that is currently rented to a great tenant! This is A LOT of square footage and potential for the money! You know what to do...make an appointment before it gone!
